  "text": "All the results presented here are based on a subset of the DeepSig dataset specifically BPSK, QPSK, 8PSK and 16QAM (DeepSig classes 3, 4 ,5, 12). We applied the FGSM attack using the CleverHans library [CITATION_1] . We compared results with and without the attack using Auto-encoder (AE) based training and conventional training of the convolutional neural network (CNN) presented in Figure 4 .",
